        "description": "Creates a new agent, stores its policy file under a UUID-suffixed filename, and registers the agent with AgentDNA. Fails if an agent with the same `org_id` and `agent_name` already exists, or if AgentDNA registration fails (in which case the on-disk artifacts are rolled back)."
